                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10102" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1502</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">667 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">技术赋能，流量裂变：小米汽车破界突围的营销密码</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Technology empowerment, traffic explosion: The marketing code for Xiaomi Auto&#39;s breaking boundaries and achieving breakthrough success</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">唐文秀，张杰铭，张天一，陈涛</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小米科技有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“双碳”目标；小米集团；AIoT生态；跨界转型；互联网思维；生态协同效应</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The &quot;Dual Carbon&quot; goals; Xiaomi Group; AIoT ecosystem; Cross-sector transformation; Ecosystem synergy</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020年以来，在能源安全与“双碳”目标的双重驱动下，我国新能源汽车产业迎来政策红利期。随着《新能源汽车产业发展规划（2021－2035年）》等政策落地，构建智能汽车体系的国家战略加速推进。小米集团凭借其AIoT生态优势与技术积累，敏锐捕捉到这一产业变革机遇，于2021年正式宣布跨界造车。本案例系统梳理了小米汽车从战略决策到营销破局的完整路径，重点剖析小米如何将互联网思维注入传统汽车营销：从“雷军个人IP打造”到“社交媒体病毒式传播”，从“生态产品矩阵”到“线上线下融合的新零售模式”，构建了一套完整的数字化营销体系。通过对小米汽车营销策略的拆解，为科技企业跨界转型提供可复制的营销方法论，同时，本案例深度适用于探讨粉丝经济与个人IP营销，以及在此基础上的基于流量的病毒式营销策略，为理解数字化转型时代的用户运营与传播规律提供了典型范本。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Since 2020, driven by both energy security and the &quot;Dual Carbon&quot; goals, China&#39;s new energy vehicle (NEV) industry has entered a period of policy dividends. With the implementation of policies such as the &quot;New Energy Vehicle Industry Development Plan (2021–2035)&quot;, the national strategy of building an intelligent vehicle system has accelerated. Leveraging its AIoT ecosystem and technological expertise, Xiaomi Group keenly identified this industrial transformation opportunity and officially announced its entry into automotive manufacturing in 2021. This case study systematically examines Xiaomi Auto&#39;s complete journey from strategic decision-making to marketing breakthroughs, focusing on how Xiaomi infused internet thinking into traditional automotive marketing—ranging from building Lei Jun&#39;s personal IP to viral social media dissemination, and from an ecosystem product matrix to an online-offline integrated new retail model—establishing a comprehensive digital marketing system. By deconstructing Xiaomi Auto&#39;s marketing strategies, it provides replicable methodologies for technology companies undergoing cross-sector transformation. Meanwhile, this case is deeply applicable to the exploration of fan economy and personal IP marketing, as well as the viral marketing strategies based on traffic on this basis, providing a typical model for understanding the user operation and communication rules in the era of digital transformation.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《市场营销》、《品牌管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">病毒式营销;4P营销理论;创新扩散理论;AAARR理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
